    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、すみれ。こんな所にいたのか\nわざわざ屋上に来て、何か気になることがあったのか？",
      "startTime": 4.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "高層ビルの屋上からだと、遠くまでよく見えるなぁ\n……ん？　あそこの人、何してるんだろ",
      "startTime": 14.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "うわ！？\nそんなに柵から身を乗り出したら危ないぞ！！",
      "startTime": 19.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 533.3329519000004,
          "startTime": 19.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ、{user}さん？\nそんなに慌ててどうしたんですか？",
      "startTime": 25.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんでって、すみれが屋上から落ちそうになってたら\nそりゃ、焦りもするだろう！？",
      "startTime": 31.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　私が屋上から落ちる？\n……あ、地上にいる人を見てたからかな",
      "startTime": 36.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "あそこを歩いてた人が、なんだか妙な動きをしてたので\n気になって、思わず下を覗き込んじゃったんです",
      "startTime": 45.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "でも大丈夫ですよ。ほら、柵はしっかり握ってますし\n絶対に手を離したりはしませんから",
      "startTime": 54.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ならいいけど、事故には本当に気を付けてくれよ\nそれにしても、なんで一人で屋上なんかに来たんだ？",
      "startTime": 61.5,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
